# AEM block CSS

- Scope all selectors under `.{blockname}` (or `header` / `footer` where appropriate)
- Use theme tokens: `--accent-color`, `--surface-color`, `--text-muted`, etc.
- Mobile-first; enhance at 600px / 900px / 1200px
- Prefer flex/grid; avoid fixed desktop-only widths
- Match existing portfolio visual language (dark cards, cyan accents)
